{"id": "1500481214065283283", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "固有(専用装備等)はないです！\nそのキャラをモチーフにした札が各キャラに1枚あるので、それですねー", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T12:56:39.026000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500481548074356877", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "なるほど。それはやはり限定ガチャで排出ですか？", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T12:57:58.660000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500481939805573151", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "限定キャラのモチーフ札は限定ガチャ。\n恒常キャラのモチーフ札は恒常ガチャですね。", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T12:59:32.056000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500482155896246313", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "ありがとうございます。", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T13:00:23.576000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500482272376131736", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "そろそろ落ちなくてはいけないのですが、最後にもうふたつほど。", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T13:00:51.347000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500482383391232030", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "対人戦と幻夢の深奥はやっておいた方がいいですか？", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T13:01:17.815000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500482728314011770", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1492114990147178606", "author_name": "tianmoheizi_16992", "content": "深奥はなんとかなっているのですが、対人戦がどうも勝手がわからず、特にドラフトモードが難しいです。", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T13:02:40.051000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500487903778705418", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "専門外なので他の方ー", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T13:23:13.978000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500509174784725004", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1129096201887821844", "author_name": "ugen_22zi", "content": "両方自由に", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T14:47:45.381000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500509223564480594", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1129096201887821844", "author_name": "ugen_22zi", "content": "報酬欲しいとか、なら頑張って", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T14:47:57.011000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500509318691291206", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1129096201887821844", "author_name": "ugen_22zi", "content": "俺はダルいし、対人バケモンばっかで勝てねぇから辞めた", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T14:48:19.691000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500511626183577620", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "content": "幻夢怠いのでやってないですね…", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T14:57:29.840000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500511872250675351", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "content": "対人戦は普段のイベントだとか高難度だとか融災だとかの合間に息抜きでやってます。", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T14:58:28.507000+00:00"}
{"id": "1500511919109443684", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "content": "自由にやろう！", "timestamp": "2026-05-03T14:58:39.679000+00:00"}
